{
    "ai-thag14.1:0.1_0": "Verses of the Senior Monks",
    "ai-thag14.1:0.2_0": "The Book of the Fourteens",
    "ai-thag14.1:0.3_0": "Chapter One",
    "ai-thag14.1:0.4_0": "and in the Moreover, greover,",
    "ai-thag14.1:1.1_0": "Since I’ve gone forth",
    "ai-thag14.1:1.2_0": "the home life for homelessness",
    "ai-thag14.1:1.3_0": "I’m not aware of any intention",
    "ai-thag14.1:1.4_0": "ignoble, malicious intentions.",
    "ai-thag14.1:2.1_0": "“May these beings be killed!",
    "ai-thag14.1:2.2_0": "May they be slaughtered! May they suffer!’—",
    "ai-thag14.1:2.3_0": "I’m not aware of having any such intentions",
    "ai-thag14.1:2.4_0": "in all this long while.",
    "ai-thag14.1:3.1_0": "I have been aware of loving-kindness,",
    "ai-thag14.1:3.2_0": "measureless and well-developed;",
    "ai-thag14.1:3.3_0": "gradually consolidated",
    "ai-thag14.1:3.4_0": "as it was taught by the Buddha.",
    "ai-thag14.1:4.1_0": "I’m friend and comrade to all,",
    "ai-thag14.1:4.2_0": "compassionate for all beings!",
    "ai-thag14.1:4.3_0": "I develop a mind of love,",
    "ai-thag14.1:4.4_0": "delighting in harmlessness.",
    "ai-thag14.1:5.1_0": "Unfaltering, unshakable,",
    "ai-thag14.1:5.2_0": "I gladden the mind.",
    "ai-thag14.1:5.3_0": "I develop the divine meditation,",
    "ai-thag14.1:5.4_0": "which sinners do not cultivate.",
    "ai-thag14.1:6.1_0": "Entering meditation without thought,",
    "ai-thag14.1:6.2_0": "Soṇa, a disciple of the Buddha,",
    "ai-thag14.1:6.3_0": "The noble ones are silent,",
    "ai-thag14.1:6.4_0": "while still a lay follower.",
    "ai-thag14.1:7.1_0": "Supported by the rocky mountain",
    "ai-thag14.1:7.2_0": "well established,",
    "ai-thag14.1:7.3_0": "A mendicant who has ended delusion",
    "ai-thag14.1:7.4_0": "a monk, like a mountain, doesn’t tremble.",
    "ai-thag14.1:8.1_0": "who has a blemish and does,",
    "ai-thag14.1:8.2_0": "always seeking purity,",
    "ai-thag14.1:8.3_0": "Bones up a evil,",
    "ai-thag14.1:8.4_0": "seems as big as a cloud.”",
    "ai-thag14.1:9.1_0": "Just like a frontier city,",
    "ai-thag14.1:9.2_0": "guarded, inside and out;",
    "ai-thag14.1:9.3_0": "Look yourself like this,",
    "ai-thag14.1:9.4_0": "don’t let the moment pass you by.",
    "ai-thag14.1:10.1_0": "“I don’t long for death;",
    "ai-thag14.1:10.2_0": "“I don’t long for life.",
    "ai-thag14.1:10.3_0": "I’m enjoying the time for time,",
    "ai-thag14.1:10.4_0": "like a worker waiting for their wages.”",
    "ai-thag14.1:11.1_0": "“I don’t long for death;",
    "ai-thag14.1:11.2_0": "…",
    "ai-thag14.1:11.3_0": "pe…",
    "ai-thag14.1:11.4_0": "aware and mindful.",
    "ai-thag14.1:12.1_0": "“I’ve served the teacher",
    "ai-thag14.1:12.2_0": "and fulfilled the Buddha’s instructions.”",
    "ai-thag14.1:12.3_0": "one who is heavy,",
    "ai-thag14.1:12.4_0": "the attachment to rebirth is eradicated.”",
    "ai-thag14.1:13.1_0": "But one who has gone forth",
    "ai-thag14.1:13.2_0": "the home life for homelessness",
    "ai-thag14.1:13.3_0": "from the lay life to homelessness:",
    "ai-thag14.1:13.4_0": "the end of all fetters.”",
    "ai-thag14.1:14.1_0": "Persist with diligence:",
    "ai-thag14.1:14.2_0": "this is my instruction;",
    "ai-thag14.1:14.3_0": "I’ll become fully extinguished.",
    "ai-thag14.1:14.4_0": "I’m liberated in every way.",
    "ai-thag14.1:14.5_0": "... with a senior monk raped a senior monk ..."
}